- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with representation learning, which is a common topic in AI research. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses geometric transformations in embedding space, which is relevant to image processing and computer vision. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also less likely but possible as the paper deals with neural network models and their ability to learn relationships in embedding space.
